channel.title: What happened? Lol
channel.description:
So I decided to take a look at good ol' DeltaScape. Browsing through the announcements and found this...
[code]Deltascape Will return!
However, the normal server will not be returning.
This is going to be a Player Killing based server. If everything goes right it should be up by the end of this week or a little later.
Thank you for voting on the poll and expressing all of your opinions
Also, please post here what items you don't want to be spawnable.
If you know the ID post that too, if not it's okay
Thanks.
-The deltascape staff __________________[/code]
Personally, I :FP: at this.... Anyone agree?
